sentences: In the conclusions (FCCC/SBSTA/2004/L.22), SBSTA, inter alia, notes the paper on options for enhanced cooperation among the three Rio Conventions and requests the Secretariat to make the outcome of the consideration of the JLGs paper available to the first SBSTA session following the JLGs meeting.
